content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4220.12 - Limitation on use of stable names

State Regulations

An individual or partnership can not file as a stable
name one which has been already filed or one which is the name of a race horse
or one which is the real name of an owner of race horses. Notes
